query:
INSERT INTO "UserHistory" ("userId", "itemId", "itemType", "createdAt", "updatedAt")
        SELECT u.user_id, u.item_id, 'chat', NOW(), NOW()
        FROM UNNEST($1::text[], $2::text[]) AS u(item_id, user_id)
        ON CONFLICT ("userId", "itemId", "itemType") DO UPDATE
        SET "updatedAt" = NOW();
